{"tid":2234374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美懲教人員用《Baby Shark》狂轟囚犯 被控虐待罪","createTime":"2020-10-08T00:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T09:12:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f48f942a00caac3c725e4503a421b3d17161b16f","tid":2234374,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:23:32.000Z","msg":"邁爾斯向律師表示，這首兒歌只是他和畢拿之間的「一個玩笑」。不過，當地地方檢察官普拉特（David Prater）認為，三人以「殘忍或不人道」方式，合謀﹑故意及錯誤地對囚犯進行懲罰，而反覆播放這首兒歌，為正在遭受痛苦的囚犯帶來不適當的情感壓力。案件中，兩名囚犯曾在睡夢中、凌晨二時及三時，被拉進房間面壁罰站被《Baby Shark》狂轟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201008/G3K5JN2WSZBJVBYFQ6IAOX3PW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2FG3K5JN2WSZBJVBYFQ6IAOX3PW4%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5BR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=50de914e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201008%2FG3K5JN2WSZBJVBYFQ6IAOX3PW4%2F&h=43087fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201008/G3K5JN2WSZBJVBYFQ6IAOX3PW4/</a>"},{"pid":"476b8c78ef2f7b02d4e05e3eba2921364e704f06","tid":2234374,"uid":63157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:24:38.000Z","msg":"香港: 合乎指引"},{"pid":"f1548adf28f73585c9fef8ca492599f0ae499182","tid":2234374,"uid":221171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnD0cHc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnD0cHc.gif&h=58aa3fa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94f46a52e34a0b6ea4a541fb50327985e9ad4ea2","tid":2234374,"uid":79085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"港共笑左"},{"pid":"87c2e04b2fae0e5cd1ed1688ac37c0934c36aff6","tid":2234374,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94f46a52e34a0b6ea4a541fb50327985e9ad4ea2","tid":2234374,"uid":79085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,